Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:32.78,IwStTm Opening Romaji,,0,0,0,,sono ashi de yuke sono mimi de kike
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:36.23,IwStTm Opening Romaji,,0,0,0,,sono riaru wa tsukurimono deshou\N
